      "active": true,
      "full_text": "The Y to I spelling rule does not apply to the -ING ending (e.g., carry ➔ carrying; fly ➔ flying).\rIf the letter before the final Y is a vowel, the Y is part of a vowel team and does not change to I when adding a suffix (e.g., play ➔ plays; stay ➔ stayed)."
